A perfect scenery to experience wildlife and rainforest, a morning Safari Float is one of the best choices to see most wildlife. The float takes from 2.3 to 3 hours, a perfect choice for the whole family and all ages. A tropical fruit snack will be served by your guide in the middle of the journey through the river.
Next, we will drive to La Fortuna waterfall to enjoy clear pristine water surrounded by lush rainforest where you can swim and catch unforgettable sceneries in your mind.
Lunch will be included at the end of this expedition, a local family will be preparing a delicious meal for you. 
